revised_title: Obituary Notices of Fellows Deceased: John Lubbock, Baron Avebury and Philip Lutley Sclater
tldr: This article provides obituary notices for two notable fellows of the Royal Society, John Lubbock, Baron Avebury, and Philip Lutley Sclater. Both individuals made significant contributions to various scientific fields, including natural history, ornithology, entomology, and science history.
